{"slug":"sirkuler-23-126e-10661","reference":"Sirkuler_23_126E","gazette":"Official Gazette dated 28 January 2023 and numbered 32087","title":"Value-based surveillance is to applied for certain goods from glass fibers","date":"20 Mart 2023","bodyHtml":"<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><td>\r\n  <p>Value surveillance is to be applied for some goods classified in tariff\r\n  heading 7019. Products classified in the HS codes in the table below with\r\n  a unit customs value of less than US$2/gross kg are subject to\r\n  surveillance from February 27, 2023.<o></o></p>\r\n  <p>The products covered are the following.<o></o></p>\r\n  <p>-Slivers, rovings, yarn and chopped strands and mats thereof<o></o></p>\r\n  <p>-Other articles from fibers suitable for weaving<o></o></p>\r\n  <p>-Felt from glass fibers<o></o></p>\r\n  <p><a  href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2023/01/20230128-9.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Click here</b></a>\r\n  for the Communiqué on the Implementation of Surveillance on Imports (No:\r\n  2023/3).<o></o></p>\r\n  <p><o> </o></p>\r\n  <div align=\"center\">\r\n  <table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"548\">\r\n   <tbody><tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>HS Code</span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span>Item Description<u1></u1></span></b><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><span>Customs Value (USD/Kg)*<u1></u1></span></b><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.11.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Chopped strands, of a length of not more than 50 mm</span><br></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\" nowrap=\"\" rowspan=\"8\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>2<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.12.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Rovings</span><br></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.13.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Other yarn, slivers</span><br></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.14.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Mechanically bonded mats</span><br></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.15.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Chemically bonded mats</span><br></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.19.00.00.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Others<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n   <tr>\r\n    <td width=\"19%\" nowrap=\"\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span>7019.90.00.10.00<u1></u1></span><span><o></o></span></p>\r\n    </td>\r\n    <td width=\"64%\">\r\n    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Of textile fibres suitable for weaving</span><br></p>\r\n  